Author contributions
D.Y.T. Goh conceptualized and designed the study, drafted the initial manuscript, and reviewed and revised the
manuscript. M.W.M. and W.L.J. Lee designed the data collection instruments, and coordinated and supervised
data collection, carried out the initial analyses, and reviewed and revised the manuscript. O.H.T. designed the
study, collected and interpreted the data, and reviewed and revised the manuscript. D.D.R. designed the study,
interpreted the data, conducted the literature search and reviewed and revised the manuscript. All authors
approved the final manuscript as submitted and agree to be accountable for all aspects of the work.
